3195507\" /><br><br>Level up by selling goods. Each time you level up, you would earn a perk point. With those perk points, you can unlock perks that would give you an advantage while you are on your journey. There are 41 perks to choose from 2 different perk categories: Army and Trade. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382920/extras/7.png?t=1663195507\" /><br><br>You can have your own stores in the cities. You can decide the price of the goods. However, you should pay attention to the price rates of the city since the higher price means a lower probability of a sale. Each time you sell a good, you would earn some reputation. With enough reputation, you can sell your goods for even higher prices. However, it is hard to gain a reputation in the bigger cities.","developers":["Ege Say\u0131n"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382920/header.jpg?t=1663195507","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256819024,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256819024/movie480.mp4?t=1611242596","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256819024/movie_max.mp4?t=1611242596"},"name":"Gameplay Trailer 2","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256819024/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1611242596","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256819024/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1611242596","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256819024/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1611242596"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256796098,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256796098/movie480.mp4?t=1597166975","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256